VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bopen\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:request\.|input\(|argv|os\.path\.join && MISSING:os\.path\.realpath|os\.path\.abspath|startswith|allowlist|whitelist
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects file open calls that incorporate user-controlled path components.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Path Traversal: open() with User-Controlled Path.
